item.title: Who am I?
item.dc:creator: bdomanski
item.content:encoded: I'm an aspiring photographer who loves taking portraits, pictures of people and more often than not, on film. Born in a small town of yrardw in Poland and later moved to Ireland, currently studying Creative Digital Media in the Institute of Technology, Blanchardstown. As well as taking portraits I very much enjoy event and nature photography. In my spare time I love experimenting with film, it brings a whole new feeling to photography. My current equipment includes a Canon 7D, Canon 1D Mark II N with an 50mm F1.8 lens, my beloved Olympus OM10 with a wide variety of manual lenses.

item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: bdomanski
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: Film is Not Dead
item.dc:creator: bdomanski
item.content:encoded:
[embed width="123" height="456"]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9eVs41cINVM[/embed]
As part of the Second Year module called Documentary Filmmaking, we were set out on a task to film a documentary of our choice. Along with my classmate, Megan Bredin, we decided to focus on photography and interviewed the owner of John Gunns Camera Shop.
